      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of precision engineering, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This unit boasts a flawless maintenance pedigree, with recent rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacements completed as preventative measures. The chassis remains taut, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a M-Variable limited-slip differential for optimal lateral grip. Finished with a factory carbon fiber roof to lower the center of gravity, this vehicle offers a visceral, analog driving experience in showroom-quality condition. No paint correction required; the finish is concours-ready.",
